  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe encourage you to participate in the democratic process. If you are eligible to vote and require time off from work to do so, we will provide reasonable time off in accordance with applicable state and local laws. This policy outlines the conditions under which voting leave may be granted, including any notice requirements and whether the leave is paid or unpaid. We aim to ensure that you have the opportunity to exercise your right to vote.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
